  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a medium pot over medium heat.",
    "Add onion, carrot, and garlic; saut\u00e9 until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in cumin, smoked paprika, and sumac; cook 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add chickpeas, vegetable broth, and water; bring to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer for 15 minutes.",
    "Using an immersion blender, blend the soup until slightly thick, leaving some texture.",
    "Stir in Greek yogurt, whisking until well incorporated and heated through.",
    "Season with salt, pepper, and lemon juice to taste; adjust acidity if needed.",
    "Serve hot, optionally garnished with fresh parsley or a drizzle of olive oil."
  ],
